race.description: Lvtc 2025 Melbourne Cup Tickets On Sale Now Hcp
race.comment: SECURITY ADVISOR (5) showed good early speed and raced just off the lead before lifting to score by 0.9 lengths over 1900m at Kilcoy last start. Winning rider Montana Philpot stays aboard. Likely to feature. BAVARIAN LADY (7) progressed nicely last time out to finish just 1.75 lengths from the winner in second over 1890m at Toowoomba. Looks well placed so expect another big run. BORN TO BE ALIVE (8) stuck on well last start to finish second over 1800m at Gold Coast after showing good early speed. This is a nice race and can find winning form. ANOTHER DAZZLER (11) next in line in a race decimated by scratchings.
